content: Hey Sarah, just wanted to confirm I'll have the rent payment ready by the 1st as always. Already set aside the money in my savings account.
Thanks Alex! You're always so reliable with payments. Really appreciate it.
Mom, I transferred the $200 for your prescription today. Should show up in your account by tomorrow morning. Let me know if you need anything else.
Thank you sweetheart. You're so thoughtful and responsible. I'm proud of you.
Mike, I know I promised to help you move this weekend. I've already rented the truck for Saturday morning. What time should I pick you up?
